%% rhods-operator Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.24/rhods-operator.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin / User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant DSCICtrl as DSCI Controller
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controller
    participant Manifests as /opt/manifests/<br/>Kustomize Overlays
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Istio as Istio Control Plane<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ExtSvc as External Services<br/>(segment.io, PagerDuty)

    Note over Admin, ExtSvc: Flow 1: Component Enablement

    Admin->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply DSC CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-datasciencecluster<br/>TLS (serving cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-datasciencecluster<br/>TLS (serving cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated DSC
    K8sAPI-->>Admin: DSC Created

    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch event: DSC created<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Component CRs<br/>(Dashboard, Kserve, etc.)
    K8sAPI->>CompCtrl: Watch event: Component CR created
    CompCtrl->>Manifests: Read kustomize overlays
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply manifests<br/>(Deployments, Services, etc.)

    Note over Admin, ExtSvc: Flow 2: Platform Initialization

    Admin->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply DSCI CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-dscinitialization<br/>TLS (serving cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI->>DSCICtrl: Watch event: DSCI created

    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Namespace<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicies
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Auth CR
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Monitoring CR

    Note over Admin, ExtSvc: Flow 3: Service Mesh Configuration (optional)

    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshControlPlane<br/>(istio-system)
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Authorino CR<br/>(auth namespace)
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshMember
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply EnvoyFilter/AuthorizationPolicy

    Note over Admin, ExtSvc: Egress Flows

    DSCICtrl->>OAuth: Register OAuthClient<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    DSCICtrl->>ExtSvc: Usage telemetry (segment.io)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    DSCICtrl->>ExtSvc: Alerting (PagerDuty/DMS)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
